com.datamirror.ts.target.publication.userexit.datastage

Interface DataStageDataFormatIF

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SampleDataFormatForHdfs, SampleDataFormatForWebHdfs, SampleDataStageDataFormat

    public interface DataStageDataFormatIF
    This interface allows customization of the data format used when sending data to DataStage. The data format can be customized for each source table, and for both Flat File and Direct Connect mappings.
